<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1436,150,429]" box="[199,1249,330,357]" pageId="4" pageNumber="281">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,295,330,356]" pageId="4" pageNumber="281">Biology.</emphasis>
The adults of this new species can be collected on tree trunks at night (
